c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Framer and Galileo AI share a solid foundation of core features including Ai Generation, Export Formats, Responsive. Where Framer pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Templates and Drag And Drop and Brand Kit and Collaboration and Animations and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Framer holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Galileo AI scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Framer offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Galileo AI's starting price of $19/mo. Framer has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Galileo AI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
